  "html": "<!-- TODO (EJ): brand-new project page. Add your voice. Draft until ready. -->\n<p class=\"\">A personal cable channel: every visitor sees the same YouTube video at the same second. A single-file Deno app with a stateless, deterministic playhead — live at <a href=\"https://tv.tools.ejfox.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"external-link group inline-flex items-center text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400\" data-preview-url=\"https://tv.tools.ejfox.com\">tv.tools.ejfox.com</a>.</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"The channel mid-broadcast — everyone tuned to the same frame\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/tv-station/channel.png\" alt=\"The channel mid-broadcast — everyone tuned to the same frame\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/tv-station/channel.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/tv-station/channel.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/tv-station/channel.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/tv-station/channel.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"The channel mid-broadcast — everyone tuned to the same frame\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2026\" style=\"--splay-rot:2.36deg;\" data-dimensions=\"3000×2026\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">The channel mid-broadcast — everyone tuned to the same frame</figcaption>\n</figure>",
